headline: Waters Corporation Schedules Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) will hold its Q4 2025 financial results conference call on Thursday, February 12th, 2026 at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time. A live webcast of the presentation will be available on Waters Investor Relations website at https://ir.waters.com. A replay of the webcast will also be available until at least March 12, 2026, at midnight Eastern Time.
